# BEGIN GDA EXCLUDES

# CSV Export Restrictions
# I was late reading TOS seems i cant share the CSV files, or i can but i cant
# to much extra hassle i dont want. Solution, prevent CSV uploads, provide downloaders
# And before you ask why im not using there API's UKPowerNetworks is infuriating, and CSV
# are simply faster

*.csv

# GDA Specific Excludes.
# What we exclude and why

# Ignore all log files, they contain identifable data
*.log

# Ignore All TXT Files.
# I dont write TXT but if there used they contain keys, so skip them
*.txt

# DO Not publish experts.
# I have made the decision you MUST train your own experts there are lots of reasons
# the short end is the law is complex and id rather not

MachineLearning/experts/pre-trained-experts/ 
*.joblib
*_metrics.json



# END GDA EXCLUDES







